e_link;sellerN:;elmt:;cpos:69;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3VzLm5vdGhpbmcudGVjaC9wcm9kdWN0cy9lYXItc3RpY2siLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6ImQ3YzZmNTExLTlmZDYtNDM0ZS1iNTBmLTRlNDU0OTdiY2FhMyJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAXccpNemaFJNEiCd91Qo4XHjV__RPXnwnO0qkAbpp8QS&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fus.nothing.tech%2Fproducts%2Fear-stick" class="rapid-with-clickid">Nothing Ear Stick</a>在同一指南中获得了<a data-i13n="cpos:70;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-budget-wireless-earbuds-130028735.html#honorablementions">荣誉奖</a>，现在在 Nothing 的在线商店中售价降至 79 美元。对于本质上缺乏深沉低音的开放式耳塞来说，这仍然有点贵，但比平常便宜了 20 美元。</p><p>我们向那些讨厌真正入耳式耳机感觉的人推荐耳棒，因为这种开放式设计位于外耳上，而不是一直进入耳道。虽然 50 美元的<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:71;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAATfRT1BuMdEnY4g0ETExhgwLD1VZ_qkjHfVvcusel58C&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FAll-new-Echo-Buds-2023-Release-True-Wireless-Earbuds%2Fdp%2FB09JVG3TWX%2F" class="rapid-with-clickid">亚马逊 Echo Buds</a>整体价值更高，但 Ear Stick 的设计更时尚，透明的外壳可以像口红管一样旋转打开。对于这种风格的耳塞来说，其音频质量非常稳定（并且可以根据需要进行定制），而 AirPods 风格的触摸控制则易于使用。每次充电 6 小时左右，电池续航时间还过得去。请记住，这种类型的设计几乎无法阻挡外界噪音，因此它不适合飞行或拥挤的办公室。</p><h2>苹果航空标签</h2><p><core-commerce id="a8bf8d02852f4d2fa1a0749e448e49f1" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:72;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAZ15PBFyMKoCK-eTkyUolU147qP72NYQx9kVJUFsk6f-&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FApple-MX532AM-A-AirTag%2Fdp%2FB0933BVK6T%2F" class="rapid-with-clickid">Apple AirTag</a>在<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:73;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAZ15PBFyMKoCK-eTkyUolU147qP72NYQx9kVJUFsk6f-&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FApple-MX532AM-A-AirTag%2Fdp%2FB0933BVK6T%2F" class="rapid-with-clickid">亚马逊</a>和<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Walmart;elmt:;cpos:74;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=3719d8d4-5edd-4817-998a-91f3229e7323&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Walmart&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiIzNzE5ZDhkNC01ZWRkLTQ4MTctOTk4YS05MWYzMjI5ZTczMjMiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cud2FsbWFydC5jb20vaXAvQXBwbGUtQWlyVGFnLzQ3NTYzNDEzMT9zZWxlY3RlZD10cnVlIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiJkN2M2ZjUxMS05ZmQ2LTQzNGUtYjUwZi00ZTQ1NDk3YmNhYTMifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAStLwt6znxz1Bho2WXXUbf6t8BdI1sPAgf-DCtHTQ7by&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.walmart.com%2Fip%2FApple-AirTag%2F475634131%3Fselected%3Dtrue" class="rapid-with-clickid">沃尔玛的</a>售价已降至 25 美元，虽然只有 4 美元的小幅折扣，但仍然与我们今年看到的最低价格相当。 AirTag 是我们最佳 <a data-i13n="cpos:75;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-bluetooth-tracker-140028377.html">蓝牙追踪器</a>指南中​​“最适合 iPhone”的选择，因为它利用 Apple 庞大的<a data-i13n="cpos:76;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=4130e2f0-a14f-4c5e-bdab-cd52ac7d8e79&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Apple&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI0MTMwZTJmMC1hMTRmLTRjNWUtYmRhYi1jZDUyYWM3ZDhlNzkiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYXBwbGUuY29tL2ljbG91ZC9maW5kLW15LyIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiMDZmZmJmZDktNTMwZC00ZWZjLTg5NzItMjJmYWM1Y2U1ZjljIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAWfXMEsI4d3HXdVcvkSPBvtqpHbMIpKj2MgNzrHDCELj&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.apple.com%2Ficloud%2Ffind-my%2F&amp;uuid=N0pG8JICYUVdSaPJ122099">“查找我的”</a>网络和超宽带无线技术来准确定位丢失的物品。</p><p>近年来，像这样的蓝牙跟踪器肯定面临着审查，因为有<a data-i13n="cpos:77;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-airtag-brooks-nader-tracked-privacy-175938300.html">许多</a>不良行为者使用这些设备来跟踪毫无戒心的受害者的<a data-i13n="cpos:78;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-airtag-stalking-police-reports-190022315.html">案例</a>，促使苹果和谷歌开发<a data-i13n="cpos:79;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/google-rolls-out-anti-stalking-measures-for-airtag-and-other-bluetooth-trackers-194936293.html">新的反跟踪措施</a>。该设备可能会<a data-i13n="cpos:80;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-is-convinced-my-dog-is-stalking-me-143100932.html">无意中过度活跃地</a>发送警报，而且更不严重的是，它没有环形孔或内置粘合剂，无法轻松地将设备固定到钥匙扣等物体上。话虽如此，如果您拥有一部 iPhone，并且只是希望在丢失钱包、钥匙或其他任何东西时能获得额外的安心，那么 AirTag 是更好的选择之一。</p><h2>三星 Galaxy Z Flip 5 + Z Fold 5 预订</h2><p><core-commerce id="72780b2590934bb8b7e9364887daf866" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>亚马逊仍有大量三星即将推出的可折叠手机和智能手表的预购优惠。 512GB <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:81;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAATarcmua-3u9nB4nWZcRYM8ayddJIyfBBw2XFP3tOi3P&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FSAMSUNG-Storage-Unlocked-Smartphone-Foldable%2Fdp%2FB0CCC322BL" data-demonetize-referrer="https://www.amazon.com/SAMSUNG-Storage-Unlocked-Smartphone-Foldable/dp/B0CCC322BL?th=1" class="rapid-with-clickid">Galaxy Z Flip 5</a>附赠价值 150 美元的亚马逊礼品卡，售价 1,000 美元；512GB <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:82;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWE