ay-is-2200-130009839.html">巨大的 49 英寸显示屏</a>，几乎在所有方面都超出了你的想象。其曲面 QD-OLED 面板具有 32:9 的宽高比、240Hz 刷新率、5,120 x 1,440 分辨率和双内置扬声器，以及常见的色彩、对比度和响应时间优势。我们还没有亲自测试过该设备，但<a data-i13n="cpos:93;pos:1" href="https://www.pcmag.com/reviews/samsung-odyssey-oled-g9">网络</a><a data-i13n="cpos:92;pos:1" href="https://www.displayninja.com/samsung-odyssey-oled-g9-review/">上的</a><a data-i13n="cpos:90;pos:1" href="https://reviewed.usatoday.com/gaming/content/samsung-odyssey-oled-g9-review-hugely-impressive">其他</a><a data-i13n="cpos:91;pos:1" href="https://www.techradar.com/computing/monitors/samsung-odyssey-oled-g9-review-a-futuristic-monitor-with-a-backwards-ui">评论</a><a data-i13n="cpos:94;pos:1" href="https://www.pcgamer.com/samsung-odyssey-oled-g9/">一直</a>很好评。</p><p>缺点是它的成本为 2,200 美元。好多啊！不过，目前该设备可享受 400 美元折扣。显然，这与便宜相差甚远，即使以这个价格，该面板也不会像最好的非 OLED 面板那样明亮。但如果钱不是问题的话，这看起来就像目前超宽显示器一样高端，而且现在价格便宜了一点。</p><p><em>在 Twitter 上</em><em>关注</em><a data-i13n="cpos:95;pos:1" href="https://twitter.com/EngadgetDeals"><em>@EngadgetDeals</em></a>并<a data-i13n="cpos:96;pos:1" href="https://subscription.yahoo.net/Newsletter/Preference/sub?b=engadgetdeals&amp;src"><em>订阅 Engadget Deals 时事通讯，</em></a><em>了解最新的科技交易和购买建议。</em></p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/apples-macbook-air-m2-drops-to-an-all-time-low-plus-the-rest-of-the-weeks-best -tech-deals-154028563.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/apples-macbook-air-m2-drops-to-an-all-time-low-plus-the-rest-of-the-weeks-best-tech-deals-154028563.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> d7c6f511-9fd6-434e-b50f-4e45497bcaa3</guid><dc:creator>杰夫·邓恩</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Fri, 04 Aug 2023 15:40:28 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1691164688</ingested><modified> 2023-08-04T15:58:21+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Consumer Discretionary]]></category><category><![CDATA[Shopping]]></category><category>